{"_path":"/en/tech-dev/2024/08/26/cdn-content-delivery-network","_dir":"26","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"Exploring the Functionality and Applications of Content Delivery Network (CDN) | Lucas's Blog","description":"2024-08-26 Introducing the CDN architecture, functions and application scenarios, as well as implementation examples.","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"exploring-the-functionality-and-applications-of-content-delivery-network-cdn"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"className":["text-xl","font-bold"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Exploring the Functionality and Applications of Content Delivery Network (CDN)"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"traditional-website-setup"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"className":["text-lg","font-bold"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Traditional Website Setup"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In traditional website setups, website content is hosted on a single server."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"When a user clicks on a URL in their browser, it connects to DNS, which translates the URL into the website's IP address."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The browser then connects directly to that server to retrieve website content."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"Traditional Website Process","src":"https://cdn.lucas-chen.website/2024/08/26/01.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"This method has the following disadvantages:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The farther away a user is from the server, the slower the speed (especially for global websites)."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Server stability is reduced (high traffic and multiple simultaneous connections to the same server increase the chance of a server crash)."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"introduction-to-cdn"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"className":["text-lg","font-bold"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Introduction to CDN"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"This led to the development of CDN."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CDN stands for Content Delivery Network."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"It allows website content to be deployed to edge nodes at various locations."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Users from different regions can access the nearest server to retrieve content, providing several advantages:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Faster load times (reducing physical distance)."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Reduced load on the main server (users access the nearest CDN server, decreasing the load on the origin server)."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Improved reliability (multiple CDN servers reduce the risk of downtime)."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Enhanced user experience (faster connection speeds, quicker website browsing, and reduced risk of site crashes)."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CDN Process Diagram:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"CDN Process Diagram","src":"https://cdn.lucas-chen.website/2024/08/26/02.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Website content is stored on the primary server."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"After configuring CDN, when users connect to the website, they first connect to DNS."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DNS then redirects to CDN DNS."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CDN DNS identifies the user’s location and returns the IP of the closest CDN edge server."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The user connects to the nearest CDN edge server to retrieve website content."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CDN is composed of the following:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Primary content server (Origin Server)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DNS"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CDN DNS"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CDN edge servers (CDN servers distributed across different regions)"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"CDN composed","src":"https://cdn.lucas-chen.website/2024/08/26/03.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"practical-demonstration"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"className":["text-lg","font-bold"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Practical Demonstration"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I uploaded several large GIF files to a test website and placed them far from Taiwan."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Then I tested the load speed for the first time."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"CDN Demo1","src":"https://cdn.lucas-chen.website/2024/08/26/04.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"CDN Demo2","src":"https://cdn.lucas-chen.website/2024/08/26/05.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"CDN Demo3","src":"https://cdn.lucas-chen.website/2024/08/26/06.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"It took almost 3 seconds to load the images."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Then I set up CDN."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I used Cloudflare as the CDN service provider since they offer a free plan."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"CDN Demo4","src":"https://cdn.lucas-chen.website/2024/08/26/07.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"CDN Demo5","src":"https://cdn.lucas-chen.website/2024/08/26/08.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"CDN Demo6","src":"https://cdn.lucas-chen.website/2024/08/26/09.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"CDN Demo7","src":"https://cdn.lucas-chen.website/2024/08/26/10.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"After configuring, there are two main CDN DNS settings required by your domain registrar."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I purchased my domain on Gandi, so I need to configure the domain’s name servers there.\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"CDN Demo8","src":"https://cdn.lucas-chen.website/2024/08/26/11.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"CDN Demo9","src":"https://cdn.lucas-chen.website/2024/08/26/12.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"CDN Demo10","src":"https://cdn.lucas-chen.website/2024/08/26/13.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Once configured, it looks like this."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"After enabling the CDN, you can observe the significant improvement in loading speed."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"CDN Demo11","src":"https://cdn.lucas-chen.website/2024/08/26/14.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Compared to not using CDN, where each image took almost 3 seconds to load, with CDN, each image now loads in less than 200 milliseconds."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The speed has increased significantly."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How do I check if the website is using CDN?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"You can add cdn-cgi/trace to the end of the URL."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"You’ll see something like colo=KHH, indicating that it’s connected to the Kaohsiung CDN edge server."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"For users in Taipei, connecting to Kaohsiung speeds up the connection significantly!"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"CDN Demo12","src":"https://cdn.lucas-chen.website/2024/08/26/15.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CDN isn’t just for websites; it’s also used for video streaming, software downloads, and game image and video acceleration."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CDN helps improve speed and enhances the user experience."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"If there are any parts I missed, feel free to add suggestions."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Thank you all!"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"traditional-website-setup","depth":2,"text":"Traditional Website Setup"},{"id":"introduction-to-cdn","depth":2,"text":"Introduction to CDN"},{"id":"practical-demonstration","depth":2,"text":"Practical Demonstration"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:en:tech-dev:2024:08:26:cdn-content-delivery-network.md","_source":"content","_file":"en/tech-dev/2024/08/26/cdn-content-delivery-network.md","_stem":"en/tech-dev/2024/08/26/cdn-content-delivery-network","_extension":"md"}